<h3 id="what-is-a-function">What is a Function?</h3>
<p>A function is a reusable block of code that performs a specific task.
In ML projects, functions help organize code for data preprocessing,
model training, evaluation, etc., making it more readable and
maintainable.</p>
<h3 id="creating-a-function">Creating a Function</h3>
<ol type="1">
<li><strong>Define a simple function in
<code>main.py</code>:</strong></li>
</ol>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb1"><pre
class="sourceCode python"><code class="sourceCode python"><span id="cb1-1"><a href="#cb1-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co"># src/main.py</span></span>
