<h2 id="variable-scope-in-python">Variable Scope in Python</h2>
<p>Variables in Python have different scopes depending on where they are
defined.</p>
<h3 id="example">Example</h3>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb11"><pre
class="sourceCode python"><code class="sourceCode python"><span id="cb11-1"><a href="#cb11-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co"># src/main.py</span></span>
<span id="cb11-2"><a href="#cb11-2" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a></span>
<span id="cb11-3"><a href="#cb11-3" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>global_config <span class="op">=</span> {<span class="st">&quot;learning_rate&quot;</span>: <span class="fl">0.01</span>}</span>
<span id="cb11-4"><a href="#cb11-4" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a></span>
<span id="cb11-5"><a href="#cb11-5" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="kw">def</span> train():</span>
<span id="cb11-6"><a href="#cb11-6" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>    local_var <span class="op">=</span> <span class="st">&quot;training&quot;</span></span>
<span id="cb11-7"><a href="#cb11-7" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>    <span class="bu">print</span>(global_config)   <span class="co"># Accessible</span></span>
<span id="cb11-8"><a href="#cb11-8" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>    <span class="bu">print</span>(local_var)       <span class="co"># Accessible</span></span>
<span id="cb11-9"><a href="#cb11-9" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a></span>
<span id="cb11-10"><a href="#cb11-10" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>train()</span>
<span id="cb11-11"><a href="#cb11-11" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="bu">print</span>(global_config)       <span class="co"># Accessible</span></span>
<span id="cb11-12"><a href="#cb11-12" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co"># print(local_var)        # Error: not accessible outside the function</span></span></code></pre></div>
<h3 id="scope-types">Scope Types</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Global Scope:</strong> Variables defined outside
functions/classes, accessible everywhere in the file.</li>
<li><strong>Local Scope:</strong> Variables defined inside a function,
accessible only within that function.</li>
<li><strong>Function Parameters:</strong> Treated as local variables
within the function.</li>
</ul>
